latestIgtvVideos.title: @vivelbyitc ad campaign
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Happy & proud to be part of the #RespectWorkForHome campaign initiated by @vivelbyitc to celebrate the diligent , relentless and unconditional contribution of homemakers on this Women's Equality Day. Juggling roles and responsibilities , inequality of expectations continue to persist between working professionals and homemakers. ITC Vivel , with its brand philosophy of Ab Samjhauta Nahin ( No More Compromise ) takes an inclusive step forward to bridge this gap in expectations . 

Let's respect , appreciate and acknowledge one wonderful homemaker you know - share this video as your story and tag her !
Happy Women's Equality Day .
#RespectWorkForHome #absamjhautanahin 
@VivelByITC

latestIgtvVideos.title: Manorama news Pularvela
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Thank you @manoramanews and @jain_maryjohn for covering me... This was very unexpected and I am more than happy and overhwhelmed... For a new independent stylist like me it's a big platform to widen my reach.. From being a little girl who wished and hoped  my picture appeared somewhere in the media to having appeared in such an established news channel it is definitely a dream come true... This could not have happened without the love and support from my family, friends and my insta family...
